ging the traditional schedules of competitions so that they take place in cooler months or cooler times of day.\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 1262, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 961, \"end\": 963, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9953136591551225, \"rank\": 0.004707130185599655, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 942}, {\"ngram\": \"places\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 952}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 984}, {\"ngram\": \"summertime competitions\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 1009}, {\"ngram\": \"the middle\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1044}, {\"ngram\": \"the night\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1057}, {\"ngram\": \"the report's recommendations\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1136}, {\"ngram\": \"the traditional schedules\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1180}, {\"ngram\": \"competitions\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1196}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1220}, {\"ngram\": \"cooler months\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1237}, {\"ngram\": \"cooler times\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1253}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1260}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking to reporters ahead of its release, Kaitlyn Trudeau, senior research associate at Climate Central, said: \\\"Without concerted efforts to reduce carbon emissions there is no doubt that the Earth's temperatures are on a trajectory that will make it nearly impossible, if not completely impossible, to host summer Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1591, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1308, \"end\": 1315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaitlyn_(wrestler)\", \"score\": 0.9957241429440393, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kaitlyn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaitlyn_(wrestler)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaitlyn_(wrestler)\"}, {\"begin\": 1316, \"end\": 1323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Trudeau\", \"score\": 0.9999998754942758, \"rank\": 1.2450587927295965e-07, \"text\": \"Trudeau\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Trudeau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Trudeau\"}, {\"begin\": 1354, \"end\": 1369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Climate_Central\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Climate Central\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Climate_Central\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Climate_Central\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"reporters\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1285}, {\"ngram\": \"its release\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1306}, {\"ngram\": \"senior research associate\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1350}, {\"ngram\": \"concerted efforts\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1403}, {\"ngram\": \"carbon emissions\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1430}, {\"ngram\": \"no doubt\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1448}, {\"ngram\": \"the Earth's temperatures\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1478}, {\"ngram\": \"a trajectory\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1498}, {\"ngram\": \"summer Olympics\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ms Trudeau added that extreme heat combined with humidity means the body struggles to cool down, which can lead to heat-stress on bodies, dizziness, exhaustion and heat stroke.\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1769, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1596, \"end\": 1603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Trudeau\", \"score\": 0.9999998754942758, \"rank\": 1.2450587927295965e-07, \"text\": \"Trudeau\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Trudeau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Trudeau\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"extreme heat\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1627}, {\