er said he wanted the sports sector to sound an \\\"alarm bell\\\" to prevent warming as well as look at adaptation methods such as moving the schedules.\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2692, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2533, \"end\": 2540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.999814030016361, \"rank\": 0.0001843053297931648, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sports sector\", \"from\": 2563, \"to\": 2580}, {\"ngram\": \"an \\\"alarm bell\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2604}, {\"ngram\": \"warming\", \"from\": 2617, \"to\": 2624}, {\"ngram\": \"adaptation methods\", \"from\": 2644, \"to\": 2662}, {\"ngram\": \"the schedules\", \"from\": 2678, \"to\": 2691}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We need to fight for every tenth of a degree that we possibly can \\\"We need to fight for every tenth of a degree that we possibly can,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2694, \"to\": 2838, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every tenth\", \"from\": 2715, \"to\": 2726}, {\"ngram\": \"a degree\", \"from\": 2730, \"to\": 2738}, {\"ngram\": \"every tenth\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2793}, {\"ngram\": \"a degree\", \"from\": 2797, \"to\": 2805}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The climate researchers looked at how temperatures have changed since the Olympics were last hosted in Paris and France a century ago in 1924, with analysis suggesting an average 3.1C warming for those weeks in July and August.\", \"from\": 2840, \"to\": 3067, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2943, \"end\": 2948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.188888165885933e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2953, \"end\": 2959, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/